Wolcen Lords of Mayhem was inspired by Diablo 2, one of the most popular games, using the CryEngine. But this is only a small part of the features of the new project, if you look a little more closely, here is what is proposed:
- Obtaining new abilities and their subsequent development will be available to any character, regardless of class;
- Exploring a new world will allow you to get more opportunities in the game;
- Improved system for creating new items;
- Possibility of building a house;
- The latest developments in the field of AI (thanks to a profitable cooperation with Kythera).

The cyberpunk theme will always be in demand from ordinary players. And the best part is that now the creators of the legendary Witcher have turned their attention to this universe. They decided to take matters into their own hands and create a truly unique and large world to explore and enjoy the many possibilities. At the same time, you can edit the appearance of the main character, not limit your actions in the expanses of this game and do everything to find a special drug that can make its owner immortal. It will be difficult to do this, since the world in which you will live is divided by the influence of various gangs, and they will definitely not want such a curious character to go and look for treasure.
Game Features

a well-developed character editor will allow you to work well on your appearance and make it unique;

pay attention to the appearance of the main character, in most cases NPCs will react to this and treat you accordingly, so this issue should definitely be worked on well, otherwise the sad consequences will definitely not please you;

Non-linearity is also the main feature of the game, because thanks to it, you can act freely and achieve success, while the whole world will be open to your careful exploration, and additional quests will reinforce your desire to succeed;

an abundant number of implants will allow you to modify the main character in different directions, from a melee master to a unique shooter and even a hacker;

